---
title: Grilled Chicken Breast Fajitas  with Creamy Chipotle Sauce
description:  Grilled, spiced chicken breasts add a delicious smokiness to these fajitas. To make things even easier on a weeknight, grab an oven-proof pan and cook the veggies on the grill top, too!
